---
import BaseLayout from "../../../components/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../../../components/Hero.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="支持 / Support - RosterSlate" description="RosterSlate support page in Chinese and English.">
  <Hero
    compact
    kicker="RosterSlate"
    title="支持 / Support"
    zh="用于 RosterSlate App 支持、隐私问题和数据删除指引。"
    en="For RosterSlate app support, privacy questions, and data deletion guidance."
  />
  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="bilingual">
        <article class="contact-card">
          <span class="lang-label">中文</span>
          <h3>联系支持</h3>
          <p>支持邮箱：<a href="mailto:2578033436@qq.com">2578033436@qq.com</a></p>
          <p>请尽量附上 App 版本、设备型号、系统版本和简要问题描述。通常会在 3-5 个工作日内回复。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="contact-card">
          <span class="lang-label">English</span>
          <h3>Contact support</h3>
          <p>Support email: <a href="mailto:2578033436@qq.com">2578033436@qq.com</a></p>
          <p>Please include your app version, device model, system version, and a short description of the issue when possible. We usually respond within 3-5 business days.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="bilingual">
        <article class="prose-card">
          <span class="lang-label">中文</span>
          <h3>常见帮助主题</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>创建工作单位、人员和班次类型后，可以录入自己的班次或全员班表。</li>
            <li>使用“只看我”或人员筛选，快速查看自己的班次和同班人员。</li>
            <li>导入图片班表后，请先检查识别结果，再确认写入排班记录。</li>
            <li>开启通知后，可以为自己的班次设置上班前提醒。</li>
            <li>通过 App 内删除入口移除工作单位、人员、班次、提醒规则或相关数据。</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="prose-card">
          <span class="lang-label">English</span>
          <h3>Common help topics</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Create a workplace, people, and shift types before entering your shifts or full staff rosters.</li>
            <li>Use the Me view or person filters to quickly review your shifts and coworkers.</li>
            <li>After importing a roster image, review recognized results before saving them as shift records.</li>
            <li>Allow notifications to receive reminders before your shifts.</li>
            <li>Use in-app delete controls to remove workplaces, people, shifts, reminder rules, or related data when available.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
      <article class="prose-card content-stack">
        <section class="callout">
          <h3>数据与隐私 / Data and privacy</h3>
          <div class="bilingual">
            <p>RosterSlate 不需要账号即可使用。除非你主动导出或分享，排班记录主要保存在你的设备本地。</p>
            <p>RosterSlate is designed to work without an account. Roster records are stored locally on your device unless you choose to export or share them.</p>
          </div>
          <p><a href="/rosterslate/privacy/">隐私政策 / Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </section>
        <section class="callout">
          <h3>非医疗或工资服务 / Not medical or payroll services</h3>
          <div class="bilingual">
            <p>RosterSlate 是通用排班工具，不提供医疗诊断、临床决策、工资发放、税务、法律或银行服务。</p>
            <p>RosterSlate is a general roster planning tool. It does not provide medical diagnosis, clinical decisions, payroll, tax, legal, or banking services.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
